  "title": "Baker (5 days/12 hours) #OPK",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location: Redhill, One North</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Timing: 6am to 3pm</strong></li><li><strong>Working Days: 5 days</strong></li><li><strong>OT payable</strong></li><li><strong>Transport Allowance+ Machine Allowance + Sunday Allowance</strong></li><li><strong>Gross Salary around $2,800 to $3,000</strong></li><li><strong>Halal Bakery</strong></li></ul><p><strong>The Challenges:</strong></p><ul><li>Assisting the Chef in preparing and baking the muffins</li><li>Supporting MUIS / Consultant in Halal compliance check (a plus but not a must)</li><li>Inventory checking and housekeeping</li><li>Assist the counter sales of muffins and support the juice bar operations as well</li><li>Assist to do pop-up stalls at the malls as required</li><li>Willing to be rotated among the cafes and stalls according to shift roasters and schedule</li><li>Any other duties as assigned by the supervisors</li></ul><p><strong>What it Takes:</strong></p><ul><li>Require a Food & Hygiene Certificate</li><li>Able to Speak/Read/Write simple English</li><li>Able to do standing job for long hours </li><li>Willing to worked in a hawker centre environment (non air-con)</li></ul><p>Interested Applicants, please submit a copy of your updated resume (in MS Word Format) and send to sarah@talentsatwork.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Sarah</p><p>Reg No: R2198293</p><p>EA Licence No: 21C0501</p><p><br /></p><p><em>*We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidate will be notified. Thank you.</em></p>",
